# Request body samples
---
**Create new ticket with minimal mandatory field**
```
{
"viewModel": {
"TicketTypeId": "d2b1fcc4-723d-4c36-ba1a-6f91b11d5c1c",
"Clients": [{
"Id": "16cf737b-4d01-4a05-97f6-70fffacd270d"
}
],
"RequestId": "07945278-4253-4a5a-90ca-96ddf533f2c4",
"Summary": "New request created by API",
"Description": "Description of the request"
},
"lockTicket": false
}
```
---
**Update ticket Summary and description**
Call [api/Ticket/RetrieveDetails](#/Ticket/post_api_Ticket_RetrieveDetails) first to get ticket object and call
this api with updated property
```
{
"viewModel": {
// Data from api/Ticket/RetrieveDetails
},
"lockTicket": false
}
```

